hadiths[112]{hadithnumber,text}:
5430,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen cheezen aisi hain ke jis shakhs mein bhi pai jaeyn, eman us ko lazeez malum hota hai. (usey eman mein maza aaney lagta hai.) Allah aur us ka Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) usey har chiz sey ziyada piyarey hon. uski mohabbat aur narazi khalis Allah Taala key liye ho. azeem bhadakti aag mein gir padna usey Allah Taala key sath kisi ko shareek thehraney sey ziyada pasand ho."
5431,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan farmaya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs mein ye teen cheezen pai jaeyn, wo eman ki mithaas mehsus karta hai : jo shakhs kisi aadmi sey mohabbat karta hai kisi mafad key liye nahin balke sirf Allah Taala ki raza key liye. jisey Allah Taala aur us ka Rasool har chiz sey ziyada piyarey hon. jis shakhs ko aag mein kood jana kufr ki taraf lot janey sey ziyada pasand ho jab ke Allah Taala ney us ko kufr sey nikal liya hai."
5432,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan farmaya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs mein ye teen cheezen pai jaeyn, wo eman ki mithaas mehsus karta hai : jo shakhs kisi aadmi sey mohabbat karta hai kisi mafad key liye nahin balke sirf Allah Taala ki raza key liye. jisey Allah Taala aur us ka Rasool har chiz sey ziyada piyarey hon. jis shakhs ko aag mein kood jana kufr ki taraf lot janey sey ziyada pasand ho jab ke Allah Taala ney us ko kufr sey nikal liya hai."
5433,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen osaaf (khubiyan) jis shakhs mein paaiy jaeyn, wo (un ki barkat sey) Islam ki mithaas mehsus kerega. wo shakhs jis ko Allah Taala aur us ka Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) har chiz sey ziyada piyarey hon : jo kisi shakhs sey sirf Allah Taala ki raza key liye mohabbat kerey. jis shakhs ko kufr ki taraf lotna itna napasand ho jitna aag mein phenk diya jana."
5434,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : teen osaaf (khubiyan) jis shakhs mein paaiy jaeyn, wo (un ki barkat sey) Islam ki mithaas mehsus kerega. wo shakhs jis ko Allah Taala aur us ka Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) har chiz sey ziyada piyarey hon : jo kisi shakhs sey sirf Allah Taala ki raza key liye mohabbat kerey. jis shakhs ko kufr ki taraf lotna itna napasand ho jitna aag mein phenk diya jana."
5435,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : eik din hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir they ke eik aadmi hamein achcha nazar pada. uskey kapdey intehai safed they aur sar key baal intehai siyah. na to is par safar key nishaanaat nazar aatey they aur na usey koi pahchaantaa tha yahan tak ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aa kar beth gaya aur us ney apney ghutney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key ghutnon key sath laga diye. aur apni hatheliyan aap ki raanon par rakh lein phir kaha : aey Muhammad ! mujhey Islam key barey mein batlaaiyen? aap ney farmaya : ye ke to gawahi dey ke Allah Taala key siwa koi ibadat key laaiq nahin aur Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Allah Taala key Rasool hain. aur to namaz ki pabandi kerey. Zakat ada kerey. Ramzanul-Mubarak key rozey rakhey aur agar to taqat rakhey to Baitullah ka Haj kerey. us ney kaha : aap sach farmatey hain. hamein is par herani hui ke ye aap sey poochhta bhi hai aur tasdeeq bhi karta hai. phir us ney kaha : aap mujhey eman key barey mein batlaaiyen? aap ney farmaya : ye ke to Allah Taala par, uskey farishton, uski kitabon, uskey Rasulon, aakhirat ke dinpar aur har achchhi buri taqdir par eman rakhey. us ney kaha : aap sach farmatey hain. mujhey ehsan key barey mein batlaaiyen? aap ney farmaya : ye ke to Allah Taala ki ibadat is tarah karey goya usey to dekh raha hai, phir agar to usey nahin dekhta to wo tujhey dekh raha hai. us ney kaha : mujhey qiyamat key barey mein khabar dijiye? aap ney farmaya : jis sey puchha gaya hai, wo poochhney waley sey qiyamat ka ziyada ilm nahin rakhta. us ney kaha : phir mujhey uski nishaniyan batla dijiye? aap ney farmaya : (eik nishani ye hai) ke londi apni maalika ko janeygi aur (dusri) ye ke to nangey paon phirney waley, nangey jism rehney waley, bakriyon key kangaal charwaahon ko dekhega ke wo eik dusrey key muqabley mein fakhr ke andaz mein oonchi oonchi imaraten bananey lagey hain. (phir wo chala gaya) Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : teen din main isi tarah (hairan) thehra raha. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey farmaya : umr ! jantey ho wo saail kon tha? mainey kaha : Allah aur us ka Rasool hi khub jantey hain. aap ney farmaya : wo Jibril alehissalam they. tumhein tumharey deeni maamlat sikhaaney aaye they."
5436,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : eik din hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir they ke eik aadmi hamein achcha nazar pada. uskey kapdey intehai safed they aur sar key baal intehai siyah. na to is par safar key nishaanaat nazar aatey they aur na usey koi pahchaantaa tha yahan tak ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aa kar beth gaya aur us ney apney ghutney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key ghutnon key sath laga diye. aur apni hatheliyan aap ki raanon par rakh lein phir kaha : aey Muhammad ! mujhey Islam key barey mein batlaaiyen? aap ney farmaya : ye ke to gawahi dey ke Allah Taala key siwa koi ibadat key laaiq nahin aur Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Allah Taala key Rasool hain. aur to namaz ki pabandi kerey. Zakat ada kerey. Ramzanul-Mubarak key rozey rakhey aur agar to taqat rakhey to Baitullah ka Haj kerey. us ney kaha : aap sach farmatey hain. hamein is par herani hui ke ye aap sey poochhta bhi hai aur tasdeeq bhi karta hai. phir us ney kaha : aap mujhey eman key barey mein batlaaiyen? aap ney farmaya : ye ke to Allah Taala par, uskey farishton, uski kitabon, uskey Rasulon, aakhirat ke dinpar aur har achchhi buri taqdir par eman rakhey. us ney kaha : aap sach farmatey hain. mujhey ehsan key barey mein batlaaiyen? aap ney farmaya : ye ke to Allah Taala ki ibadat is tarah karey goya usey to dekh raha hai, phir agar to usey nahin dekhta to wo tujhey dekh raha hai. us ney kaha : mujhey qiyamat key barey mein khabar dijiye? aap ney farmaya : jis sey puchha gaya hai, wo poochhney waley sey qiyamat ka ziyada ilm nahin rakhta. us ney kaha : phir mujhey uski nishaniyan batla dijiye? aap ney farmaya : (eik nishani ye hai) ke londi apni maalika ko janeygi aur (dusri) ye ke to nangey paon phirney waley, nangey jism rehney waley, bakriyon key kangaal charwaahon ko dekhega ke wo eik dusrey key muqabley mein fakhr ke andaz mein oonchi oonchi imaraten bananey lagey hain. (phir wo chala gaya) Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : teen din main isi tarah (hairan) thehra raha. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey farmaya : umr ! jantey ho wo saail kon tha? mainey kaha : Allah aur us ka Rasool hi khub jantey hain. aap ney farmaya : wo Jibril alehissalam they. tumhein tumharey deeni maamlat sikhaaney aaye they."
5437,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera aur Hazrat Abu-Zar Raziallahu anhuma ney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apney sahaba mein is tarah tashrif farma hotey they ke koi ajnabi aadmi aata to wo nahin pehchan sakta tha ke aap kon sey hain yahan tak ke wo (aap ki baabat) poochhtey, is liye hamney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey ijazat talab ki ke hum aap key bethney key liye makhsus jagah bana den taake ajnabi aadmi aaye to wo bhi aap ko pehchan sakey. ijazat milney par hamney aap key liye mitti ka eik thada ya chabutra sa bana diya. aap is par tashrif farma hotey they. eik dafa hum bethey they aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bhi apney makhsus maqam par tashrif farma they ke eik intehai khoobsurat aur khushbu mein basa huwa eik aadmi aaya. uskey kapdon ko halka sa mail kuchail bhi nahin laga tha yahan tak ke us ney nichey bichhi hui chataai key kinarey key paas aa kar salam kaha aur kaha : aey Muhammad ! السلام علیکم ! aap alehissalam ney usey jawab diya. us ney kaha : aey Muhammad ! main qarib aa sakta hun? aap ney farmaya : qarib aa jao. wo bar-bar isi tarah kehta raha : aur qarib aa jaun? aur aap ney farmatey rahey : qarib aa jao. yahan tak ke us ney apna haath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key mubarak ghutnon par rakh diya aur kaha : aey Muhammad ! mujhey bataiye : Islam kya hai? aap ney farmaya. Islam ye hai ke to khalis Allah Taala ki ibadat karey aur uskey sath kisi chiz ko shareek na samjhey, namaz qaaim karey, Zakat ada karey. Baitullah ka Haj karey aur Ramzanul-Mubarak key rozey rakhey. us ney kaha : jab main ye kaam kar lun to kya main musalman ho gaya? aap ney farmaya : haan. us ney kaha : aap ney sach farmaya. jab hamney us shakhs ki ye baat suni to hamney is par tajjub kiya (poochhta bhi hai aur tasdeeq bhi karta hai.) phir us ney kaha : aey Muhammad ! farmaiye eman kya hai? aap ney farmaya : eman ye hai ke to Allah taalaa, uskey farishton, Kitabon, Nabiyon aur taqdir ko dil aur jaan sey taslim kar ley. us ney kaha : jab main ye kaam kar lunga to kya main momin ho gaya? aap ney farmaya : haan. us ney kaha : aap ney sach farmaya. phir kehney laga : aey Muhammad ! batlaaiye : ehsan kya hai? aap ney farmaya : ehsan ye hai ke to Allah Taala ki ibadat is tarah karey goya to Allah Taala ko dekh raha hai. agar to usey nahin dekhta to wo tujhey dekh raha hai. wo kehney laga : aap ney sach farmaya. phir wo kehney laga : aey Muhammad ! mujhey bataiye : qiyamat kab aayegi? aap ney sar jhuka liya aur usey kuchh jawab na diya. us ney dobara phir wohi sawal kiya. aap ney phir koi jawab na diya. us ney teesri dafa phir wohi sawal kiya. aap ney phir bhi koi jawab na diya. phir aap ney apna sar mubarak uthaya aur farmaya : jis shakhs sey qiyamat key barey mein puchha gaya hai, wo poochhney waley sey ziyada nahin janta. lekin qiyamat ki kuchh alaamaat hain jinkey sath us ka pata chal jaeyga, maslan : jab to dekhey ke bakriyon, bhedon key charwahey imaraten bananey main eik dusrey ka fakhr ke andaz mein muqabla kar rahey hain aur to nangey paon chalney waley aur nangey jism rehney waley ko zamin ka badshah baney dekhey aur dekhey ke aurten apney Malik jan'ne lagi hain (to phir qiyamat ka intizar kar). paanch cheezen aisi hain jin ko Allah Taala key siwa koi nahin janta. phir aap ney ye aayat padhi (ان اللہ عندہ علم الساعۃ . . .),''Allah hi ko qiyamat ka ilm hai . . . . . ۔'' phir farmaya : qism us zaat ki jisney Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko sachcha Nabi banaya jo rehnumai karney wala aur khush khabri deney wala hai ! tumhari tarah main bhi us aadmi ko pehchan nahin saka tha. (phir malum huwa ke) wo Jibril alehissalam they jo Dahiya Kalbi ki surat mein aaye they."
5438,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera aur Hazrat Abu-Zar Raziallahu anhuma ney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apney sahaba mein is tarah tashrif farma hotey they ke koi ajnabi aadmi aata to wo nahin pehchan sakta tha ke aap kon sey hain yahan tak ke wo (aap ki baabat) poochhtey, is liye hamney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey ijazat talab ki ke hum aap key bethney key liye makhsus jagah bana den taake ajnabi aadmi aaye to wo bhi aap ko pehchan sakey. ijazat milney par hamney aap key liye mitti ka eik thada ya chabutra sa bana diya. aap is par tashrif farma hotey they. eik dafa hum bethey they aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bhi apney makhsus maqam par tashrif farma they ke eik intehai khoobsurat aur khushbu mein basa huwa eik aadmi aaya. uskey kapdon ko halka sa mail kuchail bhi nahin laga tha yahan tak ke us ney nichey bichhi hui chataai key kinarey key paas aa kar salam kaha aur kaha : aey Muhammad ! السلام علیکم ! aap alehissalam ney usey jawab diya. us ney kaha : aey Muhammad ! main qarib aa sakta hun? aap ney farmaya : qarib aa jao. wo bar-bar isi tarah kehta raha : aur qarib aa jaun? aur aap ney farmatey rahey : qarib aa jao. yahan tak ke us ney apna haath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key mubarak ghutnon par rakh diya aur kaha : aey Muhammad ! mujhey bataiye : Islam kya hai? aap ney farmaya. Islam ye hai ke to khalis Allah Taala ki ibadat karey aur uskey sath kisi chiz ko shareek na samjhey, namaz qaaim karey, Zakat ada karey. Baitullah ka Haj karey aur Ramzanul-Mubarak key rozey rakhey. us ney kaha : jab main ye kaam kar lun to kya main musalman ho gaya? aap ney farmaya : haan. us ney kaha : aap ney sach farmaya. jab hamney us shakhs ki ye baat suni to hamney is par tajjub kiya (poochhta bhi hai aur tasdeeq bhi karta hai.) phir us ney kaha : aey Muhammad ! farmaiye eman kya hai? aap ney farmaya : eman ye hai ke to Allah taalaa, uskey farishton, Kitabon, Nabiyon aur taqdir ko dil aur jaan sey taslim kar ley. us ney kaha : jab main ye kaam kar lunga to kya main momin ho gaya? aap ney farmaya : haan. us ney kaha : aap ney sach farmaya. phir kehney laga : aey Muhammad ! batlaaiye : ehsan kya hai? aap ney farmaya : ehsan ye hai ke to Allah Taala ki ibadat is tarah karey goya to Allah Taala ko dekh raha hai. agar to usey nahin dekhta to wo tujhey dekh raha hai. wo kehney laga : aap ney sach farmaya. phir wo kehney laga : aey Muhammad ! mujhey bataiye : qiyamat kab aayegi? aap ney sar jhuka liya aur usey kuchh jawab na diya. us ney dobara phir wohi sawal kiya. aap ney phir koi jawab na diya. us ney teesri dafa phir wohi sawal kiya. aap ney phir bhi koi jawab na diya. phir aap ney apna sar mubarak uthaya aur farmaya : jis shakhs sey qiyamat key barey mein puchha gaya hai, wo poochhney waley sey ziyada nahin janta. lekin qiyamat ki kuchh alaamaat hain jinkey sath us ka pata chal jaeyga, maslan : jab to dekhey ke bakriyon, bhedon key charwahey imaraten bananey main eik dusrey ka fakhr ke andaz mein muqabla kar rahey hain aur to nangey paon chalney waley aur nangey jism rehney waley ko zamin ka badshah baney dekhey aur dekhey ke aurten apney Malik jan'ne lagi hain (to phir qiyamat ka intizar kar). paanch cheezen aisi hain jin ko Allah Taala key siwa koi nahin janta. phir aap ney ye aayat padhi (ان اللہ عندہ علم الساعۃ . . .),''Allah hi ko qiyamat ka ilm hai . . . . . ۔'' phir farmaya : qism us zaat ki jisney Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko sachcha Nabi banaya jo rehnumai karney wala aur khush khabri deney wala hai ! tumhari tarah main bhi us aadmi ko pehchan nahin saka tha. (phir malum huwa ke) wo Jibril alehissalam they jo Dahiya Kalbi ki surat mein aaye they."
5439,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kuchh logon ko maal diya lekin un mein sey eik aadmi ko kuchh na diya. Saad ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney falan aur falan ko to maal diya hai lekin falan ko kuchh nahin diya, halanke wo bhi sahibe-emaan hai. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (balke woh) musalman hai. Saad ney apni baat teen dafa dohraai. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) har dafa yehi farmatey they : (balke woh) musalman hai. phir Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kabhi-kabhi main kuchh logon ko maal deta hun jab ke un logon ko chhod deta hun jo mujhey ziyada piyarey hotey hain. main unhein kuchh nahin deta. (deta hun) is khof sey ke kahin wo jahannam mein ondhey munh na giraaey jaeyn."
5440,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kuchh logon ko maal diya lekin un mein sey eik aadmi ko kuchh na diya. Saad ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney falan aur falan ko to maal diya hai lekin falan ko kuchh nahin diya, halanke wo bhi sahibe-emaan hai. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (balke woh) musalman hai. Saad ney apni baat teen dafa dohraai. Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) har dafa yehi farmatey they : (balke woh) musalman hai. phir Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kabhi-kabhi main kuchh logon ko maal deta hun jab ke un logon ko chhod deta hun jo mujhey ziyada piyarey hotey hain. main unhein kuchh nahin deta. (deta hun) is khof sey ke kahin wo jahannam mein ondhey munh na giraaey jaeyn."
5441,"Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney maal taqseem farmaya, kuchh logon ko diya, kuchh ko na diya. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney falan falan ko diya, aur falan ko nahin diya, halanke wo bhi momin hai. aap ney farmaya : momin na kaho, musalman kaho. ibne-Shahab (Zohri) ney phir ye aayat tilawat ki : (قالت الاعراب اٰمنا),''dehati kehtey hain hum eman laye.''"
5442,"Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney maal taqseem farmaya, kuchh logon ko diya, kuchh ko na diya. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney falan falan ko diya, aur falan ko nahin diya, halanke wo bhi momin hai. aap ney farmaya : momin na kaho, musalman kaho. ibne-Shahab (Zohri) ney phir ye aayat tilawat ki : (قالت الاعراب اٰمنا),''dehati kehtey hain hum eman laye.''"
5443,"Hazrat Bishr bin Saheem (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen tashreeq ke dinon mein ye aelan karney ka hukm diya ke jannat mein sirf momin hi dakhil hoga, isi ke sath ye din khaney peeney key hain."
5444,"Hazrat Bishr bin Saheem (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen tashreeq ke dinon mein ye aelan karney ka hukm diya ke jannat mein sirf momin hi dakhil hoga, isi ke sath ye din khaney peeney key hain."
5445,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : asal musalman wo hai jiski zaban aur haath sey dusrey musalman mehfooz hon. aur asal momin wo hai jis sey logon ko apni jaan aur maal key barey mein koi khatra na ho.
5446,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : asal musalman wo hai jiski zaban aur haath sey dusrey musalman mehfooz hon. aur asal momin wo hai jis sey logon ko apni jaan aur maal key barey mein koi khatra na ho.
5447,. Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : asal musalman wo hai jiski zaban aur haath sey dusrey musalman mehfooz hon aur asal muhaajir wo hai jo un chizon ko chhod dey jin sey Allah Taala ney mana farmaya hai.
5448,. Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : asal musalman wo hai jiski zaban aur haath sey dusrey musalman mehfooz hon aur asal muhaajir wo hai jo un chizon ko chhod dey jin sey Allah Taala ney mana farmaya hai.
5449,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs hamari tarah namaz padhey aur hamarey qibley ki taraf munh karey aur hamara zibeh kiya huwa janwer khaye, wo musalman hai."
5450,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs hamari tarah namaz padhey aur hamarey qibley ki taraf munh karey aur hamara zibeh kiya huwa janwer khaye, wo musalman hai."
5451,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs musalman ho jaey aur achcha musalman ban jaey to Allah Taala uski har wo neki (us key namaey-aamaal mein) likh deta hai jo us ney apney daure-jahiliyat mein ki hoti hai. aur us ka har wo gunah maaf kar diya jata hai jo us ney is sey pehley kiya hota hai. phir uskey baad (us ko uskey aamal ka) badla milega. neki ka sawab das gunah sey saat-sau guna tak hoga aur burai ka badla burai key barabar hi hoga. haan ! Allah chahey to isey bhi maaf farma dey.
5452,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs musalman ho jaey aur achcha musalman ban jaey to Allah Taala uski har wo neki (us key namaey-aamaal mein) likh deta hai jo us ney apney daure-jahiliyat mein ki hoti hai. aur us ka har wo gunah maaf kar diya jata hai jo us ney is sey pehley kiya hota hai. phir uskey baad (us ko uskey aamal ka) badla milega. neki ka sawab das gunah sey saat-sau guna tak hoga aur burai ka badla burai key barabar hi hoga. haan ! Allah chahey to isey bhi maaf farma dey.
5453,Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kon sa Islam afzal hai? aap ney farmaya : jis shakhs ki zaban aur haath sey dusrey musalman mehfooz rahen.
5454,Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kon sa Islam afzal hai? aap ney farmaya : jis shakhs ki zaban aur haath sey dusrey musalman mehfooz rahen.
5455,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha kon sa Islam behtar hai? aap ney farmaya : to khana khilaaey aur har eik ko salam kahe, chahey pahchaantaa ho ya na pahchaantaa ho."
5456,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha kon sa Islam behtar hai? aap ney farmaya : to khana khilaaey aur har eik ko salam kahe, chahey pahchaantaa ho ya na pahchaantaa ho."
5457,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney un sey kaha : aap jihad key liye kyon nahin jatey? unhoney kaha : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : Islam ki buniyad paanch cheezen hain : gawahi dena ke Allah Taala key siwa koi mabood nahin (aur Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Allah Taala key Rasool hain.) namaz pabandi key sath padhna , Zakat ada karna, Haj karna aur Ramzanul-Mubarak key rozey rakhna."
5458,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney un sey kaha : aap jihad key liye kyon nahin jatey? unhoney kaha : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna hai : Islam ki buniyad paanch cheezen hain : gawahi dena ke Allah Taala key siwa koi mabood nahin (aur Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Allah Taala key Rasool hain.) namaz pabandi key sath padhna , Zakat ada karna, Haj karna aur Ramzanul-Mubarak key rozey rakhna."
5459,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik majlis mein mojud they. aap ney farmaya : mujh sey baiat karo ke Allah Taala ٰ key sath kisi ko shareek nahin banaogey, chori nahin karogey, zina nahin karogey, aap ney puri aayat tilawat farmaaee. (phir farmaya) jo shakhs is ehad ko pura kerega, us ka ajr aur sawab Allah Taala key zimmey hai. aur jis shakhs ney in (mazkura kamon) main sey kisi kaam ka irtikab kiya, phir Allah Taala ney is par parda dal diya to wo Allah Taala ki marzi par maqoof hoga. chahey usey azab dey, chahey maaf karey."
5460,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas eik majlis mein mojud they. aap ney farmaya : mujh sey baiat karo ke Allah Taala ٰ key sath kisi ko shareek nahin banaogey, chori nahin karogey, zina nahin karogey, aap ney puri aayat tilawat farmaaee. (phir farmaya) jo shakhs is ehad ko pura kerega, us ka ajr aur sawab Allah Taala key zimmey hai. aur jis shakhs ney in (mazkura kamon) main sey kisi kaam ka irtikab kiya, phir Allah Taala ney is par parda dal diya to wo Allah Taala ki marzi par maqoof hoga. chahey usey azab dey, chahey maaf karey."
5461,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey kuffar sey ladney ka hukm diya gaya hai yahan tak ke wo ye gawahi den ke Allah Taala key siwa koi mabood nahin aur Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Allah Taala key Rasool hain. jab wo ye gawahi den ke Allah Taala key siwa koi mabood nahin aur Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Allah Taala key Rasool hain aur hamarey qibley ki taraf munh (kar key namaz qaaim) keren, hamara zibeh shuda janwer khaeyn, hamari tarah namaz padhen to unkey jaan aur maal hum par haram hain, siwaey iske ke un par koi haq banta ho. unkey wohi huquq hongey jo musalmanon key hain aur un par wo faraaiz aaid hongey jo musalmanon par aaid hotey hain."
5462,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey kuffar sey ladney ka hukm diya gaya hai yahan tak ke wo ye gawahi den ke Allah Taala key siwa koi mabood nahin aur Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Allah Taala key Rasool hain. jab wo ye gawahi den ke Allah Taala key siwa koi mabood nahin aur Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Allah Taala key Rasool hain aur hamarey qibley ki taraf munh (kar key namaz qaaim) keren, hamara zibeh shuda janwer khaeyn, hamari tarah namaz padhen to unkey jaan aur maal hum par haram hain, siwaey iske ke un par koi haq banta ho. unkey wohi huquq hongey jo musalmanon key hain aur un par wo faraaiz aaid hongey jo musalmanon par aaid hotey hain."
5463,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Imaan ki sattar sey zayed shaakhen hain aur haya bhi eman ki eik aham shaakh hai.
5464,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Imaan ki sattar sey zayed shaakhen hain aur haya bhi eman ki eik aham shaakh hai.
5465,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eman ki sattar sey zayed shaakhen hain. un mein sey afzal kalma tohid (aur Risaalat) ki adaegi hai. aur in mein sey kam martaba raastey sey takleef-deh chiz ko door karna hai. aur haya bhi eman ki eik (aham) shaakh hai.
5466,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eman ki sattar sey zayed shaakhen hain. un mein sey afzal kalma tohid (aur Risaalat) ki adaegi hai. aur in mein sey kam martaba raastey sey takleef-deh chiz ko door karna hai. aur haya bhi eman ki eik (aham) shaakh hai.
5467,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haya eman ka aham hissa hai.
5468,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : haya eman ka aham hissa hai.
5469,Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key eik sahabi sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Ammaar (Raziallahu anhu) kinaron tak eman sey labaalab bhara huwa hai.
5470,Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key eik sahabi sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Ammaar (Raziallahu anhu) kinaron tak eman sey labaalab bhara huwa hai.
5471,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo shakhs bura kaam hota dekhey, wo usey apney haath sey khatam kar dey aur agar taqat na ho to zaban key sath rokey aur agar uski bhi taqat na rakhta ho to apney dil sey bura janey. aur ye (aakhiri darja) kamzor tareen eman hai."
5472,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo shakhs bura kaam hota dekhey, wo usey apney haath sey khatam kar dey aur agar taqat na ho to zaban key sath rokey aur agar uski bhi taqat na rakhta ho to apney dil sey bura janey. aur ye (aakhiri darja) kamzor tareen eman hai."
5473,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo shakhs burai hoti dekhey aur apney haath sey rok dey, wo (gunah sey) bari ho gaya. jo haath sey rokney ki taqat na rakhey aur zaban sey rok dey, wo bhi (gunah sey) bari ho gaya. aur jo shakhs zaban sey rokney ki taqat na rakhey lekin dil sey bura samjhey, wo bhi (gunah sey) bari hai. aur ye kamzor tareen eman hai."
5474,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo shakhs burai hoti dekhey aur apney haath sey rok dey, wo (gunah sey) bari ho gaya. jo haath sey rokney ki taqat na rakhey aur zaban sey rok dey, wo bhi (gunah sey) bari ho gaya. aur jo shakhs zaban sey rokney ki taqat na rakhey lekin dil sey bura samjhey, wo bhi (gunah sey) bari hai. aur ye kamzor tareen eman hai."
5475,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : tum duniya mein apney haq ki khatir itna nahin jhagadtey jitna jhagda momin apney Rab taala sey apney un musalman bhaiyon key barey mein kerengey jo aag mein dakhil kiye jaeyngey. wo (momin) kahengey : aey hamarey Rab ! ye hamarey wo musalman bhai hain jo hamarey sath namazen padhtey they, rozey rakhtey they aur Haj kartey they. tu ney in ko aag mein dal diya hai? Allah Taala farmaeyga : jao jinhein tum pehchantey ho, in ko nikal lao. wo jaeyngey aur unko unki Suraton sey pahchaanengey. un mein sey kisi ko nisf (aadhi) pindliyon tak aag lagi hogi aur kisi ko takhnon tak. wo in ko nikal laeyngey aur kahengey : aey hamarey Rab ! jinkey barey main tu ney farmaya tha, wo to hamney nikal liye. Allah Taala farmaeyga : in ko bhi nikalo jinkey dil main eik deenar key barabar bhi eman hai. phir farmaeyga : (un ko bhi nikalo) jinkey dil mein nisf (aadhey) deenar key barabar eman hai yahan tak ke farmaeyga : (un ko bhi nikalo) jinkey dil mein zarra bhar bhi eman hai. Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri ney farmaya : jo shakhs is hadees ki tasdeeq mein koi shak ho, wo ye aayat padh ley (ان اللہ لا یغفر ان یشرک بہ . .),''yaqinan Allah Taala ye to maaf nahin farmaeyga ke uskey sath kisi ko shareek thehraya jaey, albatta us sey kam dusrey gunah jis ko chaheyga, maaf farmaeyga . . . . . . . aakhir aayat tak.''"
5476,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : tum duniya mein apney haq ki khatir itna nahin jhagadtey jitna jhagda momin apney Rab taala sey apney un musalman bhaiyon key barey mein kerengey jo aag mein dakhil kiye jaeyngey. wo (momin) kahengey : aey hamarey Rab ! ye hamarey wo musalman bhai hain jo hamarey sath namazen padhtey they, rozey rakhtey they aur Haj kartey they. tu ney in ko aag mein dal diya hai? Allah Taala farmaeyga : jao jinhein tum pehchantey ho, in ko nikal lao. wo jaeyngey aur unko unki Suraton sey pahchaanengey. un mein sey kisi ko nisf (aadhi) pindliyon tak aag lagi hogi aur kisi ko takhnon tak. wo in ko nikal laeyngey aur kahengey : aey hamarey Rab ! jinkey barey main tu ney farmaya tha, wo to hamney nikal liye. Allah Taala farmaeyga : in ko bhi nikalo jinkey dil main eik deenar key barabar bhi eman hai. phir farmaeyga : (un ko bhi nikalo) jinkey dil mein nisf (aadhey) deenar key barabar eman hai yahan tak ke farmaeyga : (un ko bhi nikalo) jinkey dil mein zarra bhar bhi eman hai. Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri ney farmaya : jo shakhs is hadees ki tasdeeq mein koi shak ho, wo ye aayat padh ley (ان اللہ لا یغفر ان یشرک بہ . .),''yaqinan Allah Taala ye to maaf nahin farmaeyga ke uskey sath kisi ko shareek thehraya jaey, albatta us sey kam dusrey gunah jis ko chaheyga, maaf farmaeyga . . . . . . . aakhir aayat tak.''"
5477,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main eik dafa soyaa huwa tha ke (khuwab mein) dekha log mujh par pesh kiye ja rahey hain. unhoney qameesen pehan rakhi hain. baaz (to itni chhoti hain ke) pistaanon tak hi pahunchti hain aur kuchh un sey neechi hain. umr bin Khattab mujh par pesh kiye gaey to un par itni lambi qamis thi ke zamin par ghisat rahi thi. sahaba kiram ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ! aap ney iski kya tabeer farmaai hai? aap ney farmaya : deen.
5478,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main eik dafa soyaa huwa tha ke (khuwab mein) dekha log mujh par pesh kiye ja rahey hain. unhoney qameesen pehan rakhi hain. baaz (to itni chhoti hain ke) pistaanon tak hi pahunchti hain aur kuchh un sey neechi hain. umr bin Khattab mujh par pesh kiye gaey to un par itni lambi qamis thi ke zamin par ghisat rahi thi. sahaba kiram ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ! aap ney iski kya tabeer farmaai hai? aap ney farmaya : deen.
5479,"Hazrat Taariq bin Shahaab (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke eik Yahudi shakhs Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaya aur kaha : aey Ameerul-momeneen ! tumhari Kitab (Quran Majeed) main eik aayat hai jisey tum padhtey ho agar wo hum yahudiyon par nazil hui hoti to hum us (key nuzool) key din ko tiyohar bana letey. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : kon si aayat? us ney kaha (الیوم اکملت لکم دینکم . . . . . ),''aaj mainey tumharey liye tumhara Deen mukammal kar diya aur apna ehsan tum par pura kar diya aur tumharey liye Islam ko Deen key taur par pasand farmaya.''Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main us jagah ko bhi janta hun jis mein ye aayat utri hai aur us din ko bhi. ye aayat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par Arafat ke maqam par Juma Mubarak key din utri."
5480,"Hazrat Taariq bin Shahaab (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke eik Yahudi shakhs Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaya aur kaha : aey Ameerul-momeneen ! tumhari Kitab (Quran Majeed) main eik aayat hai jisey tum padhtey ho agar wo hum yahudiyon par nazil hui hoti to hum us (key nuzool) key din ko tiyohar bana letey. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : kon si aayat? us ney kaha (الیوم اکملت لکم دینکم . . . . . ),''aaj mainey tumharey liye tumhara Deen mukammal kar diya aur apna ehsan tum par pura kar diya aur tumharey liye Islam ko Deen key taur par pasand farmaya.''Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main us jagah ko bhi janta hun jis mein ye aayat utri hai aur us din ko bhi. ye aayat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par Arafat ke maqam par Juma Mubarak key din utri."
5481,"Hazrat Anas Raziallahu anhu aleh sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs sahibe-emaan nahin ho sakta yahan tak ke main usey uski aulad, maa-baap aur sab logon sey ziyada piyaaraa na ho jaun."
5482,"Hazrat Anas Raziallahu anhu aleh sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs sahibe-emaan nahin ho sakta yahan tak ke main usey uski aulad, maa-baap aur sab logon sey ziyada piyaaraa na ho jaun."
5483,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs momin nahin ban sakta yahan tak ke main usey uskey ghar aur khandan aur maal aur daulat aur sab logon sey badh kar mehbub na ho jaun.
5484,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs momin nahin ban sakta yahan tak ke main usey uskey ghar aur khandan aur maal aur daulat aur sab logon sey badh kar mehbub na ho jaun.
5485,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka irshade-giraami hai : qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! tum mein sey koi shakhs momin nahin ho sakta jab tak mein uskey nazdik uski aulad aur waliden sey badh kar mehbub na ban jaun.
5486,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka irshade-giraami hai : qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! tum mein sey koi shakhs momin nahin ho sakta jab tak mein uskey nazdik uski aulad aur waliden sey badh kar mehbub na ban jaun.
5487,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka farman mubarak hai : tum mein sey koi shakhs sachcha momin nahin ban sakta yahan tak ke wo apney bhai key liye wohi chiz pasand karey jo wo apney liye karta hai.
5488,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai ke Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka farman mubarak hai : tum mein sey koi shakhs sachcha momin nahin ban sakta yahan tak ke wo apney bhai key liye wohi chiz pasand karey jo wo apney liye karta hai.
5489,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki jaan hai ! tum mein sey koi shakhs (us waqt tak ) momin nahin ho sakta jab tak wo apney (har musalman) bhai key liye isi tarah khair aur bhalai pasand na karey jis tarah apney liye karta hai.
5490,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : qism us zaat ki jis key haath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki jaan hai ! tum mein sey koi shakhs (us waqt tak ) momin nahin ho sakta jab tak wo apney (har musalman) bhai key liye isi tarah khair aur bhalai pasand na karey jis tarah apney liye karta hai.
5491,Hazrat Zar (bin Habish) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Nabi ummi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) mujhey irshad farmaya kartey they ke tujh sey momin hi mohabbat kerega aur tujh sey munafiq hi bughz rakheyga.
5492,Hazrat Zar (bin Habish) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : Nabi ummi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) mujhey irshad farmaya kartey they ke tujh sey momin hi mohabbat kerega aur tujh sey munafiq hi bughz rakheyga.
5493,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Ansaar sey mohabbat eman ki nishani hai aur Ansaar sey bughz nifaq ki nishani hai.
5494,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Ansaar sey mohabbat eman ki nishani hai aur Ansaar sey bughz nifaq ki nishani hai.
5495,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : chaar khaslaten aisi hain ke jis shakhs mein (sab ki sab) pai jaeyn, wo (khalis) munafiq hoga aur jis shakhs mein in chaaron mein sey koi eik pai jaey, is mein nifaq ki eik khaslat hogi yahan tak ke wo usey chhod dey :  jab baat karey to jhoot boley, jab wada karey to khilaf warzi kerey, jab ehad karey to be-wafai karey, jab ladaai jhagda karey to gaali bakey."
5496,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : chaar khaslaten aisi hain ke jis shakhs mein (sab ki sab) pai jaeyn, wo (khalis) munafiq hoga aur jis shakhs mein in chaaron mein sey koi eik pai jaey, is mein nifaq ki eik khaslat hogi yahan tak ke wo usey chhod dey :  jab baat karey to jhoot boley, jab wada karey to khilaf warzi kerey, jab ehad karey to be-wafai karey, jab ladaai jhagda karey to gaali bakey."
5497,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : munafiq ki nishaniyan teen hain : jab baat karey to jhoot boley. jab wada karey to khilaf warzi kerey. jab uskey paas amanat rakhi jaey to khayanat kerey.
5498,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : munafiq ki nishaniyan teen hain : jab baat karey to jhoot boley. jab wada karey to khilaf warzi kerey. jab uskey paas amanat rakhi jaey to khayanat kerey.
5499,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey irshad farmaya tha ke tujh sey momin hi mohabbat kerega aur tujh sey munafiq hi bughz rakheyga."
5500,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mujhey irshad farmaya tha ke tujh sey momin hi mohabbat kerega aur tujh sey munafiq hi bughz rakheyga."
5501,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya teen aadaten jis mein pai jaeyn, wo munafiq hoga : jab baat karey jhoot boley.  jab uskey paas amanat rakhi jaey to khayanat karey aur jab wada karey khilaf warzi kerey. jis shakhs mein in mein sey koi eik aadat pai jaey. is mein nifaq ki khaslat rahegi yahan tak ke usey chhod dey."
5502,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya teen aadaten jis mein pai jaeyn, wo munafiq hoga : jab baat karey jhoot boley.  jab uskey paas amanat rakhi jaey to khayanat karey aur jab wada karey khilaf warzi kerey. jis shakhs mein in mein sey koi eik aadat pai jaey. is mein nifaq ki khaslat rahegi yahan tak ke usey chhod dey."
5503,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Maahe-Ramzanul-Mubarak ka qiyam eman ki haalat mein aur sawab ki niyat sey karey uskey pehley tamam gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain.
5504,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Maahe-Ramzanul-Mubarak ka qiyam eman ki haalat mein aur sawab ki niyat sey karey uskey pehley tamam gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain.
5505,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs eman ki haalat mein aur sawab ki niyat se Ramzanul-Mubarak ki raaton ka qiyam kerey. uskey sab pehley gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain.
5506,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs eman ki haalat mein aur sawab ki niyat se Ramzanul-Mubarak ki raaton ka qiyam kerey. uskey sab pehley gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain.
5507,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Ramzanul-Mubarak ki raaton mein eman ki bina par aur sawab ki niyat sey ibadat kerey. uskey sab pehley gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain.
5508,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Ramzanul-Mubarak ki raaton mein eman ki bina par aur sawab ki niyat sey ibadat kerey. uskey sab pehley gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain.
5509,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs eman key jazbey aur sawab ki niyat sey Ramzanul-Mubarak ka qiyam kerey. uskey sab pehley gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain. aur jo shakhs jazbae-emaan aur niyate-sawab key sath Lailatul-Qadr mein ibadat kerey. uskey bhi sab pehley gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain.
5510,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs eman key jazbey aur sawab ki niyat sey Ramzanul-Mubarak ka qiyam kerey. uskey sab pehley gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain. aur jo shakhs jazbae-emaan aur niyate-sawab key sath Lailatul-Qadr mein ibadat kerey. uskey bhi sab pehley gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain.
5511,"Hazrat Talha bin Ubedullah ney farmaya : eik aadmi Najad key ilaqey sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa. uskey sar key baal bikhrey huye they. uski aawaz ki bhinbhinahat to sunai deti thi magar uski baat samajh mein nahin aati thi yahan tak ke wo qarib aa gaya to pata chala ke wo Islam key barey mein poochh raha hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey farmaya : har din raat mein paanch namazen. us ney kaha : kya inkey ilawa koi aur namaz bhi mujh par farz hai? aap ney farmaya : nahin, magar ye ke to khushi sey padhey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey farmaya : aur Maahe-Ramzanul-Mubarak key rozey. us ney kaha : kya iskey ilawa bhi mujh par koi rozey farz hain? aap ney farmaya : nahin magar ye ke to khushi sey karey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uskey samney Zakat ka bhi zikr farmaya. us ney kaha : iskey ilawa bhi koi maali chiz (sadqa) mujh par farz hai? aap ney farmaya : nahin siwaey iske ke to nafl sadqa karey. wo aadmi wapis janey laga to keh raha tha : main na is sey ziyada karunga na kam. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar ye aadmi apni baat par pakka raha to kamiyab ho gaya."
5512,"Hazrat Talha bin Ubedullah ney farmaya : eik aadmi Najad key ilaqey sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa. uskey sar key baal bikhrey huye they. uski aawaz ki bhinbhinahat to sunai deti thi magar uski baat samajh mein nahin aati thi yahan tak ke wo qarib aa gaya to pata chala ke wo Islam key barey mein poochh raha hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey farmaya : har din raat mein paanch namazen. us ney kaha : kya inkey ilawa koi aur namaz bhi mujh par farz hai? aap ney farmaya : nahin, magar ye ke to khushi sey padhey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney usey farmaya : aur Maahe-Ramzanul-Mubarak key rozey. us ney kaha : kya iskey ilawa bhi mujh par koi rozey farz hain? aap ney farmaya : nahin magar ye ke to khushi sey karey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney uskey samney Zakat ka bhi zikr farmaya. us ney kaha : iskey ilawa bhi koi maali chiz (sadqa) mujh par farz hai? aap ney farmaya : nahin siwaey iske ke to nafl sadqa karey. wo aadmi wapis janey laga to keh raha tha : main na is sey ziyada karunga na kam. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar ye aadmi apni baat par pakka raha to kamiyab ho gaya."
5513,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo shakhs Allah Taala key raastey mein (jihad key liye) nikalta hai, uskey liye Allah Taala ney zamanat dey rakhi hai ke agar wo sirf mujh par eman rakhtey huye aur khalis merey raastey mein jihad karney key liye nikalta hai to main usey zarur jannat mein dakhil karunga, chahey wo (maidane-jang mein) qatl ho jaey ya usi raastey mein faut ho jaey. ya phir wo (Allah Taalaa) us ko uskey ghar wapis layega jis sey wo nikla tha jab ke us ko sawab bhi hasil hoga aur ghanimat bhi jo uskey muqaddar mein hai."
5514,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : jo shakhs Allah Taala key raastey mein (jihad key liye) nikalta hai, uskey liye Allah Taala ney zamanat dey rakhi hai ke agar wo sirf mujh par eman rakhtey huye aur khalis merey raastey mein jihad karney key liye nikalta hai to main usey zarur jannat mein dakhil karunga, chahey wo (maidane-jang mein) qatl ho jaey ya usi raastey mein faut ho jaey. ya phir wo (Allah Taalaa) us ko uskey ghar wapis layega jis sey wo nikla tha jab ke us ko sawab bhi hasil hoga aur ghanimat bhi jo uskey muqaddar mein hai."
5515,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah Taala key raastey mein (jihad key liye) nikalta hai jab ke uski niyat sirf Allah Taala key raastey mein jihad hi ki ho aur mujh par eman aur merey Rasulon ki tasdeeq hi us ko jihad par majbur kar rahi ho to Allah Taala ney zamanat dey rakhi hai ke main usey zarur jannat mein dakhil karunga ya usey uskey ghar mein wapis launga jahan sey wo jihad key liye nikla tha, ilawa sawab aur ghanimat key jo us ko miley."
5516,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs Allah Taala key raastey mein (jihad key liye) nikalta hai jab ke uski niyat sirf Allah Taala key raastey mein jihad hi ki ho aur mujh par eman aur merey Rasulon ki tasdeeq hi us ko jihad par majbur kar rahi ho to Allah Taala ney zamanat dey rakhi hai ke main usey zarur jannat mein dakhil karunga ya usey uskey ghar mein wapis launga jahan sey wo jihad key liye nikla tha, ilawa sawab aur ghanimat key jo us ko miley."
5517,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : qabila Abdul-Qais ka wafad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmate-aqdas mein hazir huwa aur kaha : hum qabila Abdul-Qais waley Rabeea ki nasal sey hain. hum hurmat waley mahiney key ilawa aap key paas nahin aa saktey. hamein kisi aham chiz ka hukm dijiye jo hum aap sey sikheyn aur wapis ja kar apney ilaqey key logon ko uski dawat den. tab aap ney farmaya : main tumhein chaar chizon ka hukm deta hun aur chaar chizon sey rokta hun : (pehli chaar cheezen ye hain) Allah Taala par eman lana, phir aap ney unkey liye eman ki tafsil bayan farmaai. is baat ki gawahi dena ke Allah Taala key siwa koi mabood nahin aur main Allah Taala ka Rasool hun. namaz pabandi sey ada karna, Zakat ada karna aur apni ghaneematon mein sey paanchwan hissa mujhey (baitul-mal mein) bhejna aur main tumhein khushk kaddu key bartanon, sabz (hara) matkey aur tarkol waley matkey sey rokta hun."
5518,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : qabila Abdul-Qais ka wafad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmate-aqdas mein hazir huwa aur kaha : hum qabila Abdul-Qais waley Rabeea ki nasal sey hain. hum hurmat waley mahiney key ilawa aap key paas nahin aa saktey. hamein kisi aham chiz ka hukm dijiye jo hum aap sey sikheyn aur wapis ja kar apney ilaqey key logon ko uski dawat den. tab aap ney farmaya : main tumhein chaar chizon ka hukm deta hun aur chaar chizon sey rokta hun : (pehli chaar cheezen ye hain) Allah Taala par eman lana, phir aap ney unkey liye eman ki tafsil bayan farmaai. is baat ki gawahi dena ke Allah Taala key siwa koi mabood nahin aur main Allah Taala ka Rasool hun. namaz pabandi sey ada karna, Zakat ada karna aur apni ghaneematon mein sey paanchwan hissa mujhey (baitul-mal mein) bhejna aur main tumhein khushk kaddu key bartanon, sabz (hara) matkey aur tarkol waley matkey sey rokta hun."
5519,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs jazbae-emaan aur sawab ki niyat rakhtey huye kisi musalman key janaazey key sath jaey aur namaze-janaza padhey, phir intizar karey yahan tak ke usey qabr mein dafn kar diya jaey to usey do qeeraat sawab milega jin mein sey har eik qeeraat uhad pahad key barabar hoga. aur jo sirf janaza padh kar wapis aa jaey, us ko eik qeeraat sawab milega."
5520,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs jazbae-emaan aur sawab ki niyat rakhtey huye kisi musalman key janaazey key sath jaey aur namaze-janaza padhey, phir intizar karey yahan tak ke usey qabr mein dafn kar diya jaey to usey do qeeraat sawab milega jin mein sey har eik qeeraat uhad pahad key barabar hoga. aur jo sirf janaza padh kar wapis aa jaey, us ko eik qeeraat sawab milega."
5521,Hazrat Saalim key walid mohtaram (Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik aadmi key paas se guzrey jo apney bhai ko ziyada haya karney ki wajeh sey daant raha tha. aap ney farmaya : rehney dey ! haya eman ka hissa hai.
5522,Hazrat Saalim key walid mohtaram (Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik aadmi key paas se guzrey jo apney bhai ko ziyada haya karney ki wajeh sey daant raha tha. aap ney farmaya : rehney dey ! haya eman ka hissa hai.
5523,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Deen aasan hai. jo shakhs Deen ko sakht banaeyga, Deen is par ghalib aa jaeyga, lihaza tum apney aamal durust rakho, darmiyaanaa raasta ikhtiyar karo, khush raho. logon par aasani karo, kuchh safar pehley pahar kar liya kar, kuchh pichhley pahar aur kuchh aakhir raat ko."
5524,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Deen aasan hai. jo shakhs Deen ko sakht banaeyga, Deen is par ghalib aa jaeyga, lihaza tum apney aamal durust rakho, darmiyaanaa raasta ikhtiyar karo, khush raho. logon par aasani karo, kuchh safar pehley pahar kar liya kar, kuchh pichhley pahar aur kuchh aakhir raat ko."
5525,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) unkey paas tashrif laye to un (Hazrat Aaisha ) key paas eik aurat bethi thi. aap ney farmaya : ye kon hai? unhoney kaha : falan aurat hai. ye (raat ko) bilkul nahin soti aur iski (nafl) namaz ka zikr karney lagin. aap ney farmaya : bas karo. itna kaam kiya karo jiski tum taqat rakhtey ho. Allah ki qism ! Allah Taala (sawab deney sey) nahin uktaaeyga yahan tak ke tum uktaa jaogey. Deen key kamon mein sey Allah Taala ko sab sey ziyada pasand wo hai jis par amal karney wala hameshgi kar sakey.
5526,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) unkey paas tashrif laye to un (Hazrat Aaisha ) key paas eik aurat bethi thi. aap ney farmaya : ye kon hai? unhoney kaha : falan aurat hai. ye (raat ko) bilkul nahin soti aur iski (nafl) namaz ka zikr karney lagin. aap ney farmaya : bas karo. itna kaam kiya karo jiski tum taqat rakhtey ho. Allah ki qism ! Allah Taala (sawab deney sey) nahin uktaaeyga yahan tak ke tum uktaa jaogey. Deen key kamon mein sey Allah Taala ko sab sey ziyada pasand wo hai jis par amal karney wala hameshgi kar sakey.
5527,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo waqt qarib hai jab musalman ka behtareen maal bakriyan hongi jin ko ley kar wo pahadi chotiyon ya baarish waley ilaqon mein chala jaeyga taake apney Deen ko fitnon sey bachaey.
5528,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : wo waqt qarib hai jab musalman ka behtareen maal bakriyan hongi jin ko ley kar wo pahadi chotiyon ya baarish waley ilaqon mein chala jaeyga taake apney Deen ko fitnon sey bachaey.
5529,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : munafiq ki misal us bakri ki tarah hai jo bakrey ki talab mein do rewadon key darmiyan rehti hai. kabhi is rewad mein jati hai, kabhi us rewad mein. us ko tasalli nahin hoti ke kis rewad key sath rahey."
5530,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : munafiq ki misal us bakri ki tarah hai jo bakrey ki talab mein do rewadon key darmiyan rehti hai. kabhi is rewad mein jati hai, kabhi us rewad mein. us ko tasalli nahin hoti ke kis rewad key sath rahey."
5531,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is momin ki misal jo Quran Majeed padhta hai, naarangi ki tarah hai jiska zaiqa bhi achchhaa hai aur khushbu bhi umda. aur jo momin Quran nahin padhta, uski misal khajoor jaisi hai jiska zaiqa to umda hai magar is mein khushbu nahin. jo munafiq Quran padhta hai, uski misal naazboo ki tarah hai jiski khushbu to achchhi hai magar zaiqa kadwa hai. aur jo munafiq Quran nahin padhta, uski misal eilwey ki tarah hai. us ka zaiqa bhi kadwa hai, khushbu bhi nahin."
5532,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya is momin ki misal jo Quran Majeed padhta hai, naarangi ki tarah hai jiska zaiqa bhi achchhaa hai aur khushbu bhi umda. aur jo momin Quran nahin padhta, uski misal khajoor jaisi hai jiska zaiqa to umda hai magar is mein khushbu nahin. jo munafiq Quran padhta hai, uski misal naazboo ki tarah hai jiski khushbu to achchhi hai magar zaiqa kadwa hai. aur jo munafiq Quran nahin padhta, uski misal eilwey ki tarah hai. us ka zaiqa bhi kadwa hai, khushbu bhi nahin."
5533,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs kamil momin nahin ban sakta yahan tak ke apney musalman bhai key liye wohi kuchh pasand karey jo apney liye karta hai. کتات الایمان ikhtitaam pazeer hui. Qazi ibne Kassar kehtey hain ke mainey Abdus-Samad Bukhaari sey suna, wo farmatey they ke Hafs bin umr jo ( hadees : 5000 mein) Abdur-Rehman bin Mahdi sey bayan kartey hain, main unhein nahin janta. haan agar wo Hafs bin Amr Rabaali hon jo umuman Basriyon sey riwayat kartey hain to wo qabile-bharosa raawi hain. Qazi kehtey hain ke mainey unhein ye kehtey huye bhi suna : main nahin janta ke Anas bin Malik sey marfooa riwayat : (امرت ان اقاتل . . . .) (واستقبلوا قبلتنا . . . . . ) key izaafey key sath siwaye Abdullah bin Mubarak aur Yahya bin Ayub Misri key kisi ney Humed Taweel sey bayan ki ho. aur wo isi juz (hissey) mein (باب Ali (Raziallahu anhu) مایقاتل الناس) key tehat guzar chuki hai."
5534,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi shakhs kamil momin nahin ban sakta yahan tak ke apney musalman bhai key liye wohi kuchh pasand karey jo apney liye karta hai. کتات الایمان ikhtitaam pazeer hui. Qazi ibne Kassar kehtey hain ke mainey Abdus-Samad Bukhaari sey suna, wo farmatey they ke Hafs bin umr jo ( hadees : 5000 mein) Abdur-Rehman bin Mahdi sey bayan kartey hain, main unhein nahin janta. haan agar wo Hafs bin Amr Rabaali hon jo umuman Basriyon sey riwayat kartey hain to wo qabile-bharosa raawi hain. Qazi kehtey hain ke mainey unhein ye kehtey huye bhi suna : main nahin janta ke Anas bin Malik sey marfooa riwayat : (امرت ان اقاتل . . . .) (واستقبلوا قبلتنا . . . . . ) key izaafey key sath siwaye Abdullah bin Mubarak aur Yahya bin Ayub Misri key kisi ney Humed Taweel sey bayan ki ho. aur wo isi juz (hissey) mein (باب Ali (Raziallahu anhu) مایقاتل الناس) key tehat guzar chuki hai."
5535,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : das cheezen insan ki fitrat ka taqaza hain : munchhein kaatna, nakhun tarashna, ungliyon key jodon aur poron ko achchhi tarah dhona, dadhi puri rakhna, miswak karna, naak mein pani chadhana (aur naak ki safai karna) baghlon key baal ukhedna, sharmgah key baal mundna, pani key sath istinja karna. Musab bin Sheeba (hadees ke raawi) ney kaha : daswin chiz main bhool gaya. ummid hai ke wo kulli karna hoga."
5536,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : das cheezen insan ki fitrat ka taqaza hain : munchhein kaatna, nakhun tarashna, ungliyon key jodon aur poron ko achchhi tarah dhona, dadhi puri rakhna, miswak karna, naak mein pani chadhana (aur naak ki safai karna) baghlon key baal ukhedna, sharmgah key baal mundna, pani key sath istinja karna. Musab bin Sheeba (hadees ke raawi) ney kaha : daswin chiz main bhool gaya. ummid hai ke wo kulli karna hoga."
5537,"Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) Temi sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Talaq bin Habib ko farmatey suna, das cheezen fitri hain : miswak karna, munchhein kaatna, nakhun tarashna, ungliyon key poron aur jodon ko achchhi tarah dhona, zere-naf baal mundna, naak ki safai karna, kulli key barey mein mujhey shak hai."
5538,"Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) Temi sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Talaq bin Habib ko farmatey suna, das cheezen fitri hain : miswak karna, munchhein kaatna, nakhun tarashna, ungliyon key poron aur jodon ko achchhi tarah dhona, zere-naf baal mundna, naak ki safai karna, kulli key barey mein mujhey shak hai."
5539,"Hazrat Talaq bin Habib ney farmaya : das cheezen ( Anbiya Alaihimussalam ki) sunnat hain : miswak karna, munchhein kaatna, kulli karna, naak ki safai karna, dadhi puri rakhna, nakhun tarashna, baghlon key baal ukhedna, khatna karwana, zere-naf (sharmgah) key baal mundna aur (qazaey hajat (peshab paakhaney se faarigh honey) key baad) pusht dhona. Abu-Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) ney farmaya : Suleman (Alaihissalam) Temi ki hadees (jo is hadees sey pehley bayan hui hai) aur Jafar bin Ayaas ki mazkura (yehi) hadees Musab bin Sheba ki hadees (baab (silsile) ki pehli hadees) sey ziyada durust hai. Musab (ibne Sheba) munkarul-hadees (zaeef raawi) hai."
5540,"Hazrat Talaq bin Habib ney farmaya : das cheezen ( Anbiya Alaihimussalam ki) sunnat hain : miswak karna, munchhein kaatna, kulli karna, naak ki safai karna, dadhi puri rakhna, nakhun tarashna, baghlon key baal ukhedna, khatna karwana, zere-naf (sharmgah) key baal mundna aur (qazaey hajat (peshab paakhaney se faarigh honey) key baad) pusht dhona. Abu-Abdur-Rehman (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih)) ney farmaya : Suleman (Alaihissalam) Temi ki hadees (jo is hadees sey pehley bayan hui hai) aur Jafar bin Ayaas ki mazkura (yehi) hadees Musab bin Sheba ki hadees (baab (silsile) ki pehli hadees) sey ziyada durust hai. Musab (ibne Sheba) munkarul-hadees (zaeef raawi) hai."
5541,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : paanch cheezen fitri hain : khatna karna, sharmgaah key baal mundna, baghlon key baal ukhedna, nakhun tarashna aur munchhen chhoti karna. Imam Malik (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney is (riwayat) ko maqoof bayan kiya hai (jaisa ke agli riwayat mein aa raha hai.)"
